      "text": "DP1  [OPEN]      Navigation: Shape A (sub-page under Garments) vs Shape B (standalone nav entry, replaces Color Settings) — your call\nDP2  [RESOLVED]  Data Model: DM-B selected — first-class catalog_color_groups entity (+ catalog_color_group_preferences + catalog_brand_preferences)  |  see spike-data-model.md\nDP3  [RESOLVED]  Customer scope → V2. No customers table in DB schema. New tables designed multi-scope from day 1 (scope_type/scope_id pattern).\nDP4  [LEAN YES]  Quote Builder readiness (R7) — same tables as R1/R6, no extra schema work needed. Query interface is Wave 5.",
